snippet.title: 2nd T20 | Hindi | Highlights | India Tour Of Sri Lanka | 28th July 2024
snippet.description:
India and Sri Lanka faced each other in the 2nd T20 at Pallekele International Cricket Stadium. India won the toss and elected to bowl first. Sri Lanka started the batting well but lost their way towards the end. Sri Lanka managed to post 161 runs for the loss of 9 wickets. The match was later affected by rain and hence the target for India was 78 runs in 8 overs. India however showcased a superb batting performance and sealed a 7-wicket victory with 9 balls to spare.
.

Jaan Nisar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

7th Sky Entertainment‚Äôs mega project, Jaan Nisar, is the most awaited drama serial of the year.
The highly anticipated project marks the return of the successful on-screen couple of Danish Taimoor and Hiba Bukhari in an unforgettable love story that will steal your heart.

Nosherwan Ghaznavi, a wealthy young man, faces a pivotal moment in his life after his brother's death. This tragedy burdens Nosherwan Ghaznavi with numerous responsibilities, which he reluctantly accepts, only to find them later proving detrimental. However, his life takes a transformative turn upon meeting Dua, falling in love with her at first sight, but it places him at a critical juncture with his responsibilities.

Dua, a beautiful girl from a humble background, is raised by her parents alongside her two sisters. Despite her innocence, fate subjects Dua to a string of misfortunes before encountering Nosherwan Ghaznavi. However, their meeting completely changes their lives.

Will Nowsherwan Ghaznavi find love? What challenges will he face in balancing his duties and his love for Dua? Will his responsibilities jeopardize his love for Dua? What past events have shaped Dua's life, and will they resurface to trouble her? Will Dua return Nowsherwan Ghaznavi‚Äôs love?

Maruthi Nagar Subramanyam Theatrical Trailer 

In Cinemas August 23rd.

Buckle up, because Maruthi Nagar Subramanyam has landed, and he's bringing the ultimate laugh riot!

Thabitha Sukumar Presents

snippet.title: Exclusive: FM Nirmala Sitharaman Replies To Tough Questions On Why She Raised Tax
snippet.description:
#BTBudgetRoundTable2024 #nirmalasitharaman #middleclassfamily #tax 
At the #BudgetRoundTable2024 conference, Rahul Kanwal, Executive Director, Business Today; Sourav Majumdar, Editor, Business Today and Siddharth Zarabi, Managing Editor, BTTV engaged in an insightful conversation with Finance Minister Nirmala Sitharaman. The discussion focused on the recent tax hikes on various asset classes, including stocks, futures and options (F&Os), and the indexation of real estate. FM Sitharaman explained that the tax increases are minimal and aimed at rationalizing the tax system across different asset classes. She emphasized that measures such as indexation in the real estate sector were taken to ensure fair treatment across asset classes. FM Sitharaman assured that tax simplification remains a priority despite new changes, highlighting the GST's role in streamlining the tax structure nationwide. She clarified the hikes from 10% to 12.5% on stocks are not intended to boost government revenue but to achieve a more balanced tax framework. The government's aim is to maintain stability while simplifying taxes for broader economic¬†equity.


#taxes #equity #governmentbudget

localized.title: Exclusive: FM Nirmala Sitharaman Replies To Tough Questions On Why She Raised Tax
localized.description:
#BTBudgetRoundTable2024 #nirmalasitharaman #middleclassfamily #tax 
At the #BudgetRoundTable2024 conference, Rahul Kanwal, Executive Director, Business Today; Sourav Majumdar, Editor, Business Today and Siddharth Zarabi, Managing Editor, BTTV engaged in an insightful conversation with Finance Minister Nirmala Sitharaman. The discussion focused on the recent tax hikes on various asset classes, including stocks, futures and options (F&Os), and the indexation of real estate. FM Sitharaman explained that the tax increases are minimal and aimed at rationalizing the tax system across different asset classes. She emphasized that measures such as indexation in the real estate sector were taken to ensure fair treatment across asset classes. FM Sitharaman assured that tax simplification remains a priority despite new changes, highlighting the GST's role in streamlining the tax structure nationwide. She clarified the hikes from 10% to 12.5% on stocks are not intended to boost government revenue but to achieve a more balanced tax framework. The government's aim is to maintain stability while simplifying taxes for broader economic¬†equity.


#taxes #equity #governmentbudget

snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony LIV Channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/sonyliv
 
Click here to watch all highlights: https://bit.ly/3OVl9LM

Click here to watch more: https://www.sonyliv.com/sports/cricket-india-tour-of-sri-lanka-1700000759

Click here to subscribe now: https://bit.ly/3Q78rHU

India and Sri Lanka faced each other in the 2nd T20 at Pallekele International Cricket Stadium. India won the toss and elected to bowl first. Sri Lanka started the batting well but lost their way towards the end. Sri Lanka managed to post 161 runs for the loss of 9 wickets. The match was later affected by rain and hence the target for India was 78 runs in 8 overs. India however showcased a superb batting performance and sealed a 7-wicket victory with 9 balls to spare.

These clips and extracts are of a minimal nature and the use is not intended to interfere in any manner with their commercial exploitation of the compete work by the owners of the copyright. The use of works are in compliance with the fair dealing exception provided under Sec. 52 of the Copyright Act, and we asset our use of the works under the exception provided for criticism and review.

snippet.description:

Singer & Artist: Super Star Vikram Thakor

Ho... Valamiya...

Ven Na Bol Kadva Valam Dalde Mara Vage Chhe
Chhella Mara Swas Sudhi Prit Tari Mange Chhe
Ho Yad Rakhje Gori Taru Gomde Pan Koi Chhe


Ho Padar Na Pipade Mane Khobale Poni Pati
Sathe Rehvana Kol Didha Ta Bhuli Na Re Jati
Ho Ho... Evo Vichar Karsho Nahi Tamne Bhuli Jaishu
Kathan Kalaja Kari Valam Juda Thai Ne Rahishu
Ho Mane Chhodi Jata Shid Upadashe Pag Tara
Tara Vagar Rokai Jashe Dil Na Re Dhabkara
Ho Jiv Nathi Dur Thavano Aa Karame Dado Chhe
Jiv Nathi Door Thavano Aa Karme Dado Chhe
Kem Re Bhulu Valam Tu Mara Jiv Thi Valo Chhe
Ho... Yad Rakhaje Gori Taru Gomade Pan Koi Chhe


Ho Valaje Vali Veli Joje Modu Na Re Thay
Jiravashe Nai Tari Judai Jiv Maro Lai Jay
Ho O... Aavu Na Re Bolo Valam Aankh Radi Jay
Tari Chhu Ne Tari Revani Tane Kem Bhulay

snippet.description:
Mr. Wrong also called Bay Yanlis is a Turkish Drama in Urdu Dubbing

üéâ Subscribe   @Urdu1Officialchannel     Youtube Channel and don't forget to click the Bell icon , you'll be the first to know about our new uploads, behind-the-scenes content . Join us on this journey, and let's create amazing memories together!

 #urdu1 #MRWrong #BayYanlis

Join Ezgi, a woman with a tumultuous romantic past, and her new neighbor Asghar, a charming playboy, in a whirlwind of emotions as they navigate the complexities of love and friendship. 

Ezgi's relentless pursuit of the perfect partner often leads to heartbreak, as she prioritizes her partners above herself. Enter Asghar, whose carefree attitude towards relationships offers a fresh perspective. When Asghar offers to coach Ezgi in finding lasting love, their initial friendship takes an unexpected turn. 

As they embark on this journey together, they'll discover hidden desires and confront their own insecurities. Will their unspoken attraction blossom into something more, or will their differences drive them apart? 

Tune in to witness the highs and lows of their emotional rollercoaster as they learn valuable lessons about love, friendship, and self-discovery. Don't miss out on the heartwarming story of Ezgi and Asghar as they unravel the mysteries of the heart.

snippet.title: North Indian Vs South Indian Food Eating Challenge üî•|| FoodieWe 24hrs Challenge
snippet.description:
North Indian Vs South Indian Food Eating Challenge || Foodiewe 24hrs Challenge
1000 Rupees Challenge 

Welcome to another exciting food challenge on FoodieWe! üéâ This time, we're diving deep into the vibrant flavors of South Indian and North Indian cuisines. Mukti has set a thrilling challenge for Onkar and Aditya: survive on just ‚Çπ1000 for an entire day! But there's a twist‚ÄîAditya must savor only South Indian delicacies, while Onkar enjoys the rich tastes of North Indian fare.


From crispy dosas and spicy sambars to buttery naans and flavorful curries, this video is packed with mouthwatering and tempting dishes that will leave you craving more. Watch as Onkar and Aditya navigate their budgets, explore the diverse culinary landscapes, and compete to see who can eat the most delicious food.

Warning: Do not watch this video if you're hungry‚Äîresisting these tantalizing treats will be nearly impossible! üçõüç≤

Join us on this culinary adventure and find out who will emerge victorious in the ultimate food challenge. Don't forget to like, comment, and subscribe to FoodieWe for more epic food battles and delicious content!

#FoodChallenge #FoodieWe

Location 

1) Preet ( Time Till 2pm )- phase 7 mohali
2) Sardaji Dahi Bhalli (Time 11 am)- 3b1 Mohali
3) Shardai - 3b2 Mohali ( opp market near park )
4) nagpal - sector 34 chandigarh 
5) brother kulcha - sector 9 chandigarh 
6) gol gappe & jalebi - sector 32 street vendors market

snippet.title: Gully Bonalu || Neeraj Bandari || Chandu Charms || Telugu Short Films 2024 || Infinitum Media
snippet.description:
"Gully Bonalu" takes you on an immersive journey through the local streets and alleys (gullies) of Telangana during the vibrant Bonalu festival. This film captures the spirit and fervor of the celebrations as experienced by the local communities, showcasing their unwavering devotion and cultural richness.

Watch:- Gully Bonalu || Neeraj Bandari || Chandu Charms || Telugu Short Films 2024 || Infinitum Media 

Cast: Neeraj Bandari, Chandu Charms, Uma Mahesh, Actor Bhargav, Chandra Bhanu, Naveen Darga, Yashwanth.

Produced by Vandana Bandaru

Written & Directed by Neeraj Bandari

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.
